<li>Wallace, David, 2008, &ldquo;Philosophy of Quantum
Mechanics&rdquo;, in <em>The Ashgate Companion to Contemporary
Philosophy of Physics</em>, Dean Rickles (ed.), Aldershot, Hants,
England: Ashgate Publishing, pp. 16&ndash;98.</li>
</ul>
</div> 

